00:00:17.152 --> 00:00:18.944
<b>It is smart to seek advice early.</b>

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:21.760
<b>And follow your company’s injury reporting policy.</b>

00:00:22.528 --> 00:00:27.904
<b>You can use the Safety In Motion System to make some small practical changes </b>
<b>that reduce the stress on your body. </b>

00:00:28.928 --> 00:00:30.976
<b>Start by thinking about a Smart Setup.</b>

00:00:31.488 --> 00:00:34.304
<b>Where can you use tools and equipment to make the task easier?</b>

00:00:35.072 --> 00:00:39.168
<b>Then make some small changes in your physical technique </b>
<b>that improve your leverage,</b>

00:00:39.424 --> 00:00:40.192
<b>your strength,</b>

00:00:40.448 --> 00:00:41.472
<b>and your balance.</b>

00:00:41.728 --> 00:00:45.312
<b>And, finally, don’t forget to take a few minutes </b>
<b>to re-energize throughout the day.</b>

